duce the cost, size, and environmental impacts of\nwind farms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2010 17:36:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2010 17:42:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2011 04:08:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-27"}
