f this\neffective theory is a modified speed of sound for the adiabatic mode which is a\nfunctional of the background inflaton trajectory and the turns traversed during\ninflation. Hence in addition, we expect non-Gaussian signatures directly\nrelated to the features imprinted in the power spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2010 19:38:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2010 21:02:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2011 11:34:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 26 May 2011 02:12:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
