 $\\mu_B$, has been\nachieved with the KKR-CPA calculations by considering a chemical disorder on\nsites B, C and D.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Oct 2010 11:18:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
